OL,3,CSocial worker charged in investigation
OL,4,Cinto abuse at former children's centre
OL,6,FTwo more people have been charged in
OL,7,Fthe investigation into allegations of
OL,8,Fchild abuse at a former children's
OL,9,Fcentre in Abergavenny.
OL,11,FThe offences relate to child abuse and
OL,12,Fneglect and are alleged to have taken
OL,13,Fplace at Coed Glas Assessment Centre.
OL,15,FA 59-year-old woman, who is a social
OL,16,Fworker employed by Caerphilly County
OL,17,FBorough Council, has been charged with
OL,18,Ffour counts - whilst a 55-year-old man
OL,19,Fhas also been charged with two counts.
