OL,3,CSocial worker charged in investigation
OL,4,Cinto abuse at former children's centre
OL,6,FBoth defendants are from Caerphilly
OL,7,Fand are due to appear at Newport
OL,8,FMagistrates Court on Thursday, 12
OL,9,FFebruary.
OL,11,FIt comes after two other men denied
OL,12,Fcommitting dozens of child sexual
OL,13,Foffences at the centre between the
OL,14,F1970s and 1990s. They appeared before
OL,15,FMerthyr Tydfil Crown Court in August
OL,16,F2025.
OL,18,FAngus Riddell, 69, and Robin
OL,19,FGriffiths, 65, were charged with 45
OL,20,Foffences between them relating to 16
OL,21,Fvictims.
