OL,6,FBoth men are currently on bail and
OL,7,Fwill not appear on trial until 18
OL,8,FJanuary 2027.
OL,10,FOperation Spinney has been
OL,11,Finvestigating reports made by a number
OL,12,Fof men and women of sexual and
OL,13,Fphysical abuse committed against them
OL,14,Fas children. The charges relate to 18
OL,15,Fvictims.
