OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Andrew
OL,7,FTuck of Gwent Police said: "Operation
OL,8,FSpinney has so far brought more than
OL,9,F50 criminal charges against four
OL,10,Fpeople relating to the former
OL,11,Fchildren's home in Abergavenny.
OL,13,F"Our focus remains on securing justice
OL,14,Ffor the victims in this investigation
OL,15,Fand supporting them alongside
OL,16,Fspecialist agencies.
OL,18,F"We continue to work closely with the
OL,19,FCrown Prosecution Service and local
OL,20,Fauthorities as part of this long-
OL,21,Frunning investigation.
